2704  few combat-necessary somatics until we get the new system fully
2705  in place.
2706 
2707  Basically the idea here, is that the magnitude of the effect is
2708  enveloped over time. So after a delay, the effect begins to grow
2709  in strength until it reaches a peak. After cresting the peak the
2710  strength weakens to a fraction of the peak strength. It remains
2711  fixed there until the effect begins to wear off completely.
2712 
2713  Notes:
2714  If latency == duration the affected is a carrier.
2715 
2716 */
